casebody.data:
Friday, August 28, 1992

MOTION DOCKET

92-1495. State ex rel. Timson v. Bowman.

In Mandamus. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for a writ of mandamus. Upon consideration of relator’s motion for temporary restraining order,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that said motion for temporary restraining order be, and the same is hereby, denied, effective August 27, 1992.

Douglas, J., would grant an alternative writ.
